  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Special Northern Pacific rates\neast to points on the Missouri river\nand the middle west, to be given on\ntickets today and tomorrow for the\naccommodation of jamestown fair\ngoers, were cancelled yesterday by\nA. M. Cleland, general passenger\nagent. The action is said to be due\nto failure to obey the law requiring\na 30 day notice before such rates\nare offered.\n\n\nThe o. r. & N. was not affected\nand tickets are being sold under\nthese rates today."
    }
  ]
